Only use ui/src/theme/breakpoints.ts + useLayoutConfig() for breakpoints
Only use values from ui/src/theme/theme.ts for color/spacing
Never inline responsive styles or hard-code theme values
Theming: Use createTheme(isDark), theme.colors.brand.* (never hardcode colors)
Docs: Update existing sections; keep flow; avoid duplicates
Extend/modify existing functions/modules; uphold single-responsibility; avoid duplication
Keep API signatures; test incrementally; avoid breakage
Prefer established libs; check existing solutions before custom code
Keep Portal for z-index overlays; never drop valid usage
Know component intent before suggesting removal; ask if unsure
Build/deploy: GitHub Actions (.github/workflows/)
Firestore indexes: Manual (firebase deploy --only firestore:indexes)